    {
      "id": "0121ac55-e1e8-444d-b6f7-ad22c9beb410",
      "name": "Korn 400",
      "brand": "FILMRISS",
      "iso": 400,
      "format": "35mm",
      "type": "Black & White",
      "expiration_date": "2027-01-01",
      "created_at": "2025-08-22T07:13:16.717",
      "user_id": "335461ec-7719-4c39-b023-c600e11d308c",
      "count": 2,
      "notes": "Korn 400 is a respooled black-and-white film based on the proven Fomapan 400 Action film – ideal for those who want to remain flexible even in difficult lighting conditions. This panchromatically sensitized film was developed for applications with high mobility and variable light conditions. It offers a classic look with pronounced yet pleasing grain and good sharpness.\n\nWith its higher sensitivity (ISO 400), grain 400 is particularly suitable for street photography, reportage, interiors, or cloudy days. Even with push development, it still delivers consistent results—with increased contrast and distinctive character.\n\n \n\nISO\nBox: ISO 400\nRecommended: ISO 250-320\n\nprocess\nStandard black and white process (Rodinal, ID-11, HC-110, XTOL, etc.)\nPush up to ISO 800 or 1600 possible with appropriate development\n\nThe development times for Fomapan 400 apply\n\nDX code\n\nWe use recycled film cartridges – therefore no reliable DX code is available.",
      "price": 2.99,
      "updated_at": "2025-08-22T07:13:16.717+00:00",
